  'A small-group day-trip from Seoul to Korea''s most-loved national park and the East Sea coastal city of Sokcho. The route pairs Seoraksan''s granite peaks, valleys, and Buddhist heritage with the seafood market and beach of Sokcho — a mountain-and-ocean combination only the east coast offers. 12 hours with English-speaking guide and round-trip transport.',
